blockprints.download_desc: Download a schematic using a code from Blockprints.io
blockprints.discord: Join the Discord for support or show off your builds!
blockprints.website: View and download new builds at BlockPrints.io! Make your builds public to show them off here!
blockprints.name: Enter Name
blockprints.start_selecting: Interact with a block to select a corner.
blockprints.change_to_public: You can make this build public and downloadable at blockprints.io by editing it from your favorites list.
blockprints.cannot_contact: Could not contact Blockprints. Check your internet connection and try again.
blockprints.upload_failed: Failed processing upload. Please check log.
blockprints.download_failed: Download failed. Check your internet connection and try again.
blockprints.build_list_desc: View your builds and favorites across any world
blockprints.error_loading: We had trouble loading that. Please check your internet connection and try again. If this persists, reach out to the discord for help.
blockprints.unexpected_error: Unexpected error occured with message %s. If this persists, reach out to the discord for help.
blockprints.download_tooltip: Download the structure file to your local instance.
blockprints.blocks_missing_tooltip: Blocks used in this build are missing. View the block list to see which blocks are missing.
blockprints.make_public_tooltip: Checking this will allow other users to view and download your build from Blockprints.io. If this is disabled, you can still share your build via the code in View Builds.
blockprints.delete_tooltip: Delete this build from Blockprints.io. This action cannot be undone.
blockprints.already_downloaded_tooltip: This file has already been downloaded at %s. Download it again?
blockprints.visualize_list_tooltip: Manage, remove, and edit placed visualizations.
blockprints.start_placing: Right click to anchor to a position, use %s and %s to rotate. Press %s to confirm or %s to cancel.
blockprints.invalid_upload: Invalid build. Cannot be empty or contain only air blocks.
blockprints.move_horizontal_description: Hold Control + Scroll to move in the direction you are facing.
blockprints.move_vertical_description: Hold Control + Scroll to move up and down.
blockprints.rotate_description: Hold Control + Scroll to rotate the structure 90 degrees.
blockprints.print_description: Places the structure in the world. (Creative Only)
blockprints.confirm_description: Dismisses the management tool and keeps the visual in the world.
blockprints.delete_description: Deletes the visual and closes the GUI.
